{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "迦道夫（Fes限定Ver.） 第3话 圣都的种种不公",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "数年前 圣都格拉姆斯 王宫",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "为了找到新的工作，\\n我拜访了当年交好的格拉姆斯国王。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "得知勒福克斯灭亡原委的他\\n向我表示了同情，\\n并帮我找到了工作与住处。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "久闻“闪狼迦道夫”大名。\\n您能答应做我们的特别顾问\\n真是令我们深感荣幸。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "过奖了。\\n我没你说得那么了不起。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我听陛下说，格拉姆斯的治安\\n是由教会骑士团负责维持的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "您可能已经有所耳闻，\\n此地由伊莉雅教会掌控着实权。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "所以关于治安方面的权限\\n也归属于教会骑士团。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "但即便如此，在国家的立场上，\\n也不能没有一个维持治安的组织……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（说白了，近卫队其实是为了\\n维护国家颜面的摆设吗。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "您刚来这里，还不太熟悉吧？\\n如果您不嫌弃，\\n我可以带您参观一下格拉姆斯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "真是太感谢了。\\n不过不知我能否带上我的女儿一起？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈，你要跟紧我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "最里面的建筑就是格拉姆斯大圣堂。\\n那里只有高等圣级的人才能进去。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "圣级……教会制定的身份阶级对吧？\\n据说圣级的高低决定了\\n人所拥有的权利和权限。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "而提升圣级这一需求，\\n则有助于激励人们行善。\\n据说这是教会的理念。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "可是提升圣级的主要方法却是\\n向教会捐款。这样的话，\\n不就只有少部分人才能提升圣级了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "祸从口出……\\n这个疑问您还是藏在心里比较好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "即便您是陛下的客人，\\n但如果被教会视为异端，\\n也是会被逐出此地的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（如果这就是这个国家的规矩……\\n那我的确不适合发表意见。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "咦？话说您女儿怎么不见了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "啊！席菈！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈，原来你在这里啊。\\n我不是说过要跟紧我吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "不过这里是怎么回事？\\n离那么美丽的街道只有咫尺之遥，\\n却落魄成这个样子……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "这里是“贫民窟”……\\n是那些生活窘迫、无依无靠的人，\\n还有流民们聚集的地方。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "这里照不到阳光，对健康不利。\\n建筑也都非常破旧啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "教会的理念应该是为所有人\\n带来救赎才对，难道他们\\n不了解这个地区的现状吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "他们只是视而不见而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "对于因圣级制度产生的待遇差别，\\n人们多多少少都会有些不满。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "为了缓解这种不满，\\n教会才会一直对“贫民窟”视而不见。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "为了让人产生\\n还有人比自己过得更差，\\n所以自己很幸福的错觉吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "陛下对于“贫民窟”的现状\\n也感到非常痛心。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "可是只要教会还掌握着\\n格拉姆斯的实权，\\n我们就无法插手这件事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（得不到教会的援助，\\n也无法通过提升圣级\\n来摆脱贫困。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（住在这里的人们被迫接受着\\n不公平的待遇。教会的做法\\n虽然有效，却如此扭曲……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "怎么了，席菈……嗯？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "那个孩子在看我们呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "小朋友，有什么事吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120062_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贫民窟的少女",
            "context": "那、那个，士兵叔叔。\\n街上的墙破了个洞，\\n想请您帮忙把它补好……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "街上的墙？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "她说的应该是外围的城墙吧。\\n因为这个地区位于\\n格拉姆斯的最外围。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120062_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贫民窟的少女",
            "context": "我们自己修补了很多次，\\n可因为没有人懂得怎么补，\\n每次都补不好。所以……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "城墙不完整的话，\\n魔兽很有可能趁机入侵。\\n有必要派人来修补啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "保护格拉姆斯的城墙也在\\n教会骑士团的管辖之下，\\n我去联系他们吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120166_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "我们确实发现城墙有残缺。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120166_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "但缺口还没有大到\\n能让魔兽通过的程度。\\n这点问题不用管也没事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "等缺口扩大后就来不及了，\\n怎么想都该立刻补上吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120166_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "你是叫迦道夫对吧？\\n看你是个新来的，\\n我就教教你吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120166_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "圣都一切事宜都由教会决定，城墙的\\n修缮自然也是教会出钱。你们近卫队\\n就是个摆设，有什么资格指手画脚？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "但我不能对可能导致\\n魔兽入侵的隐患视而不见。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120166_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "你这可是越权行为。\\n再多嘴的话可别怪我请示\\n开除你并将你逐出圣都哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "近卫队长",
            "context": "如果教会正式提出要求，\\n王国也只能服从。\\n迦道夫大人，我们还是退一步吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（置弱者于不顾，并将牺牲\\n视作理所应当的这个城市\\n让我心生疑问。不过……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "是我多管闲事了……\\n我为自己的失礼道歉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120166_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "教会骑士",
            "context": "真是的，你明白就好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120062_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贫民窟的少女",
            "context": "叔叔，\\n墙壁……没法修吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "抱歉……\\n我似乎帮不了你们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "席菈，晚饭做好了。\\n一起来吃吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "（因为近卫队并无实权，所以特别顾问\\n也很少有工作。只要让席菈待在家里，\\n有什么事情我也能马上赶回来。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_100042_02_02_0060",
